{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They hang by the hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had-- we were tied up by the hand, and we had to be hung.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he had to report this to his superior.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, he made an appell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That means a gathering for all the people in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had to watch when we get hung, because if somebody was punished, all the people had to watch.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when they made the appell, the commandant for the camp and the lageralteste, and all the big shots came, and they see me over there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They know what I am doing, you know, why?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So five people-- it was the commandant, the lageralteste, his vice-president [INAUDIBLE], and the commandant from the [GERMAN] with his second man, and my kapo.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Five people went up to the hauptsturmfuhrer-- he was in charge of the camp-- and asked them for our lives.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he told them, how come?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We hung here so many people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We shot so many people, and you never put your life to ask for, you know, for someone else's life, just for them because they got the [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That means got the black market, you know, what we're making.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the lageralteste, he was a very nice person, tall person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "His name was Krakauer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was from Krakow, and his name was Krakauer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, no, that's not true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They're not the [SPEAKING GERMAN], because they are the people that are giving the food to all the people in the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We think these people really can't do the work for you because we don't have enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And thanks to these people that we can do the work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're not taking any money from nobody, because they don't need any money.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
